high_descs: Exit the bedroom through the doorway on the left, then head to the white dining table just ahead and to the right.
Pick up the loaf of bread closest to you, nearer the center of the table.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Use the microwave on the loaf of bread and take it back out.
Go back to the bedroom you came from and turn right from the entrance to the side table.
Place the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread on a bedroom side table.

high_descs: exit from the room turn right go straight turn left again turn right to reach near to diningtable
Pick the bread from the table.
Place the food item near to the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave oven, close it, set the timer for 5 minutes, wait, and then open the microwave oven.
exit from the room turn right and go reach the sidetable
Place the bread into the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Collect the bread inside outside of the oven and place it on the SideTable.

high_descs: walk from the bedroom to the diningtable
pick up the bread from the table
take the bread and walk towards the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave, power on and take out the bread.
walk left to the bedroom towards the sidetable
Set the bread on the sidetable.
